kapitan_zur_see_von_bremm02/19/24
September 11st, 1940: By Textual Order of the Regent, the "Lunarian Army Corps for Dotramese" is created, also known as the "Lunarian Dotramese Corps" (LDC), "Runarian Dottoramēze Gundan" (in Jovian) or the "Lunarisches Dotramese-Korps" (in Prussian), (This Last Name for the Organization and Uniforms used, which are reminiscent of those of the DAK [Deutsches Afrika Korps] and the colonial troops of Matthias Kellter), This Special Corps of the Grand Lunarian Army, composed of 35,000 troops, and equipped with The new CBC-38C tanks (Also known as Cruiser Tanks) and with Self-propelled Howitzers and Mortars, will be deployed in support of the Karemian troops in Dotramese, Commanded by the Daughter of the Regent and Ginga, Ayami Komura-Hikari, 22 Years of Age, better known as Ayami Bremm, since her personality and some of her physique are reminiscent of the Father of the Lunarian Nation, Fernando Bremm...
kapitan_zur_see_von_bremm02/24/24
August 29th, 1945: Lunaria manages to reestablish contact with the LDC (Lunarian Dotramese Corps) and with the Regent's Daughter, currently the LDC serves as mercenaries to obtain fuel and supplies, of the 35,000 men that made up the force before the War, only 20,000 remain, and the Most are local recruits...
